data.description: This is a 5-bedroom 3-full bath home with a 3-car garage in the Eleanora community with a beautiful Craftsman exterior.  This energy-efficient home with upgrades has so much to offer! The first floor has 1 bedroom and a full bathroom, and the upper level has 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms.  The oversized master bedroom suite has a soaking tub and separate shower for total relaxation. The laundry is located on the upper level. This is a perfect home for entertaining inside and outside. The home will include outside furnishings of patio set and gazebo in the backyard, all kitchen appliances, and the washer & dryer. The interior furniture is available for sale.
